playstore_details.title: Garner Health
playstore_details.description:
Garner is a healthcare benefit that pairs with your health insurance plan to help you find the top 20% of medical providers, called Top Providers, in the app. Garner identifies Top Providers through an analysis of over 60 billion medical records representing more than 310 million unique patients.

Top Providers are highlighted in the Garner Health app with a green Top Provider badge and represent the best available doctors near you who are in your network and have appointment availability.

Garner is funded by employers to reduce out-of-pocket medical costs and help employees stay healthy. Results have shown that employees who use Garner and see Top Providers save an average of 27% per episode of care. 

Provider recommendations are based solely on independent analysis, not commissions or fees. Garner has no financial relationships with doctors.

android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO (dangerous): record audio - Allows application to access the audio record path.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION (dangerous): coarse (network-based) location - Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.
